}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== This ''Connect and Charge'' hub doesn't even include a power adapter.
"UA034001 V1.1" is silkscreened on the board. :The '''Genesys Logic''' hub IC package is marked with "GL850G", "HH7ID08G22". :The device is using '''YDSG''' capacitors.
The power adapter that comes with the hub seems to be an ''unbranded'' YFAF24085001-05 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.5A -> 5VDC 2.5A).
